10631700@unknown@formal@none@1@S@===Ontology libraries===@1@2@@oe@30-11-2008
10631710@unknown@formal@none@1@S@The development of ontologies for the Web has led to the apparition of services providing lists or directories of ontologies with search facility.@1@23@@oe@30-11-2008
10631720@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Such directories have been called ontology libraries.@1@7@@oe@30-11-2008
10631730@unknown@formal@none@1@S@The following are static libraries of human-selected ontologies.@1@8@@oe@30-11-2008
10631740@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* The [http://www.daml.org/ontologies/ DAML Ontology Library] maintains a legacy of ontologies in DAML.@1@13@@oe@30-11-2008
10631750@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* The [http://protegewiki.stanford.edu/index.php/Protege_Ontology_Library Protege Ontology Library] contains a set of owl, Frame-based and other format ontologies.@1@16@@oe@30-11-2008
10631760@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* [http://www.schemaweb.info/ SchemaWeb] is a directory of RDF schemata expressed in RDFS, OWL and DAML+OIL.@1@15@@oe@30-11-2008
10631770@unknown@formal@none@1@S@The following are both directories and search engines.@1@8@@oe@30-11-2008
10631780@unknown@formal@none@1@S@They include crawlers searching the Web for well-formed ontologies.@1@9@@oe@30-11-2008
10631790@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* [[Swoogle]] is a directory and search engine for all RDF resources available on the Web, including ontologies.@1@18@@oe@30-11-2008
10631800@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* The [http://olp.dfki.de/OntoSelect/ OntoSelect] Ontology Library offers similar services for RDF/S, DAML and OWL ontologies.@1@15@@oe@30-11-2008
10631810@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* [http://www.w3.org/2004/ontaria/ Ontaria] is a "searchable and browsable directory of semantic web data", with a focus on RDF vocabularies with OWL ontologies.@1@22@@oe@30-11-2008
10631820@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* The [http://www.obofoundry.org/ OBO Foundry / Bioportal]is a suite of interoperable reference ontologies in biology and biomedicine.@1@17@@oe@30-11-2008
